{"article_id":"qoYeLung6ykZMCat","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The IRS official at the center of a scandal over alleged targeting of conservative groups says in a new interview","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"that her personal political leanings never impacted her work .","depth":4},{"id":2,"text":"\" I didn ' t do anything wrong , \"","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Lois Lerner told Politico in an interview","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"published Monday ,","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"her first","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"since the scandal broke more than a year ago .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"\" I ' m proud of my career and the job","depth":5},{"id":8,"text":"I did for this country . \"","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Lerner was drummed out of the agency","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"and became a lightning rod for conservative criticism","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"after reports detailed","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"how the tax agency gave extra scrutiny to conservative political groups","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"seeking nonprofit , tax-exempt status .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"Later reports showed","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"liberal groups were also given extra scrutiny ,","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"but the issue quickly became a political headache for the Obama Administration .","depth":5},{"id":17,"text":"Congressional Republicans","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"investigating the matter","depth":6},{"id":19,"text":"have accused Lerner of letting her liberal political leanings influence her work ,","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"but she was unapologetic in the interview .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"Get The Brief .","depth":3},{"id":22,"text":"Sign up","depth":4},{"id":23,"text":"to receive the top stories","depth":5},{"id":24,"text":"you need to know right now .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"Choose your country","depth":4},{"id":26,"text":"United States of America","depth":5},{"id":27,"text":"Afghanistan Albania","depth":6},{"id":28,"text":"Algeria American Samoa Andorra","depth":8